posting_body: ['Available Move-In Dates: 9/06 - 9/13 UNIT #330', 'Welcome to Waterstone-Metro', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 43', 'OR Text', '43', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 670 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Waterstone at Metro is the best place to live in the Culver City and Cheviot Hills Areas.', 'Our cozy, modern, luxury apartments make your life comfortable and simple.', 'The building is located just off the 10 freeway, near where the 405 meets.', 'Our apartments are newly remodeled and feature fresh hardwood flooring throughout your living space, stainless steel appliances, high ceilings, and quiet interiors privately disengaged from the hustle and bustle of the city around us.', 'Features:', 'Air conditioning, Carpet flooring (bedrooms only), Stainless Steel Appliances, Green Initiatives, Modern kitchens and baths, Mirrored wardrobe doors, Nest Central AC (in select homes), 9 Foot Ceilings, Dishwashers, Garbage disposal, Private balconies (in select homes)', 'Community Amenities:', '24 Hour Fitness Center, Intercom Access, Bike Repair Station, Stainless Steel BBQ Grills, 6 Laundry Facilities, 3 Resident Courtyards, Roof Top Deck with Panoramic City Views, Pet Friendly, Hydro Pool and Hot Tub, Resident Parcel Lockers, Gated Garage Parking', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets allowed.', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
